This file contains not only functionnalities to add,
but also all the implemented ones (historic),
sometimes in a verry detailed way

States
	* : done
	/ : working on that
	- : to do

Priorities
	X : Important
	M 
	S : Not verry important

Debug defines
	DEBUG_MAIN
	DEBUG_POPUP_WARN
	DEBUG_SOURCE
	DEBUG_CONTAINER
	DEBUG_DATA_PICTURE
	DEBUG_DATA_CACHE
	DEBUG_DATA_RSS
	DEBUG_DATA_RSS_PARSER
	DEBUG_DATA_FILE

Debug compil
	make install CFLAGS="-g -Wall -DDEBUG_MAIN -DDEBUG_POPUP_WARN -DDEBUG_SOURCE -DDEBUG_CONTAINER
	-DDEBUG_DATA_PICTURE -DDEBUG_DATA_CACHE -DDEBUG_DATA_RSS -DDEBUG_DATA_RSS_PARSER -DDEBUG_DATA_FILE"

